# Google Places API (New)
# 1. Acesse: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Habilite: Places API (New), Maps JavaScript API, Geocoding API
# 3. Crie uma API Key e cole abaixo
# 4. No Netlify: Site Settings > Environment Variables > adicione GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
